title: Lunchbox Gets BAD News From A Psychic + Amy vs. Lunchbox Championship! + Bobby Feud: Famous Mike’s

description:
Lunchbox was trying to prank a psychic…but it took a turn that none of us were expecting. It’s the championship round of our trivia game Amy vs. Lunchbox! Things get interesting when we play a round of the hardest category in Bobby Feud.
